description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the live July match up between The Dragons and Team Ice.
The Dragons are undefeated in Tag Team Action. Experts predict this team to win it all this year. Holly Heart has proven herself to be the best rookie in the tag Team league this year. Pair her with the 7 season veteran like Dragon Lily and you have an almost unstoppable combination.
Team Ice is led by last years Ultimate Surrender champion Ariel X. Mellanie Monroe's rookie year has been a great one. This team has lost only one match and is looking to knock the Dragons off their high horse.
The first round pits The Dragon against Ariel X. These two have never faced off in competition before. Their first meeting on the mat will set the tone for the entire match. After 12 minutes of grueling Tag Team action, only 24pts separate these two powerhouse teams. Team Ice takes the lead going into the locker room after round one.
title: ROUND One: The Dragon's (2-0) vs Team Ice (1-1)
